<pre>
&lt;p class="rh">&lt;i>Miranda v. Arizona&lt;/i> in Context&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>&lt;i>Miranda v. Arizona&lt;/i> in Context&lt;/h2>
</pre>

CSS:

<pre>
 @top-center {
   content: element(heading);
   }

 p.rh {
   position: running(heading);
   }

 p.rh::before {
   content: counter(page) ' / ';
